1
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:13,000
"Double Helix"

2
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:19,600
Bro...

3
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:21,560
I... I can't feel my legs.

4
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,376
I'm never going to walk again, am I?

5
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,400
Don't say that.

6
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:25,720
This is just a small town.

7
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,696
Once we get to a bigger hospital,

8
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:29,040
they can run more thorough tests.

9
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,120
That's right.

10
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:32,160
Cheng Yi-chen, it's going to be okay.

11
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:33,320
Don't be scared.

12
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:36,640
So... which hospital are we going to?

13
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,000
What about Mom?

14
00:01:38,001 --> 00:01:39,240
I'll take care of Mom.

15
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:42,160
No matter which hospital you go to,

16
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,900
you just listen to what Qin Lang says.

17
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:59,160
Calm down.

18
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,280
Calm down.
This is a hospital.

19
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:01,400
Don't cause a scene.

20
00:03:01,401 --> 00:03:02,679
What are you going to do?

21
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,800
Why are you so worked up?

22
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,079
You tell me.

23
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:05,800
You need to calm down.

24
00:03:05,801 --> 00:03:07,680
How are you going to hurt me?

25
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,000
What is it now?

26
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:11,040
Xiao Chen.

27
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,720
He said Cheng Yi-chen's legs are broken.

28
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,200
That can't be right.

29
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:18,880
He's lying to me, isn't he?

30
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:21,280
I just came here to apologize to her.

31
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,480
I didn't know she...

32
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,360
Mom!

33
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:26,800
Are you okay?

34
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,880
Get a doctor!

35
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,000
Doctor! Doctor!

36
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:31,040
Get out.

37
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:32,520
Get out of here right now.

38
00:03:32,521 --> 00:03:34,559
Xiao Chen, I swear I didn't
mean for this to happen.

39
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,560
Let me explain.

40
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:36,000
I really...

41
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:38,120
I just want to take
responsibility, Xiao Chen.

42
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:39,080
Listen to me.
I'm calling the police.

43
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:43,120
Someone's causing a
disturbance at the hospital.

44
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,500
(Episode 8: Fine, let's break up.)

45
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:15,200
Cheng Yi-chen! Cheng Yi-chen!

46
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:17,280
Mom.

47
00:04:18,520 --> 00:04:19,520
Mom.

48
00:04:22,080 --> 00:04:25,080
Is your brother really paralyzed?

49
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,920
Of course not.

50
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,720
Qin Lang is already abroad,

51
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:33,360
finding a good doctor for him.

52
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,800
Don't you worry.

53
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,480
He'll be fine.

54
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:47,520
Xiao Chen, my sister
arranged for my release.

55
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,320
I have to go to the US

56
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,600
to sign the papers
renouncing my inheritance.

57
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,800
Tomorrow is the deadline.

58
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,440
I'll come back for you.

59
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,520
I'll do everything I can

60
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:59,680
to heal Cheng Yi-chen's legs.

61
00:06:59,705 --> 00:07:01,061
[Blocking Lu Feng's contact info]

62
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,320
Ma'am.

63
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,080
Please, don't get up.

64
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,160
Ma'am.

65
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:20,600
Are you Cheng Yichen's girlfriend?

66
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,560
Yes.

67
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,920
I'm Cheng Yichen's girlfriend.

68
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,880
Good.

69
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,000
It's good you have a girlfriend.

70
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:04,480
Cheng Yichen, will you marry me?

71
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:09,800
I think you need a fresh start.

72
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,960
Don't you want to put
your mother's mind at ease?

73
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,720
Give yourself

74
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,600
a new chance.

75
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,280
Okay?

76
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,120
You know Lu Feng better than I do.

77
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:26,200
Sooner or later, he'll
come back and find you.

78
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,160
But I can help you.

79
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:59,360
Cheng Yichen, why didn't
Zhuo Lan come today?

80
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:01,920
Is she angry?

81
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:04,960
No, Mom.

82
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:07,600
She had something else to do today.

83
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,120
Cheng Yichen.

84
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,520
Listen to your mother.

85
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,520
Snap out of it.

86
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,640
A good girl like Zhuo Lan...

87
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:22,320
is one in a million.

88
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,640
Mom, eat first.

89
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,840
Cheng Yichen.

90
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,560
I'm dying.

91
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,800
Don't you get it? I'm dying.

92
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,440
Please, just take pity on me.

93
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,440
Don't make the same mistake again.

94
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,520
I'm begging you.

95
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,480
Xiao Chen.

96
00:09:46,160 --> 00:09:47,160
Mom.

97
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:50,880
Zhuo Lan and I are getting married.

98
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:53,800
Really?

99
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:00,080
Getting married is good.

100
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:02,280
It's good to get married.

101
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:04,480
Getting married is good.

102
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,720
Getting married is good.

103
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,280
Getting married is good.

104
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,639
Mr. Cheng Yichen,

105
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:13,720
do you take Ms. Zhuo Lan to be your wife?

106
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,520
I do.

107
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:39,880
I do.

108
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,759
Ms. Zhuo Lan,

109
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:44,360
do you take Mr. Cheng
Yichen to be your husband?

110
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,440
I do.

111
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:49,160
I do.

112
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,360
Please exchange the rings.

113
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:22,200
I have to go back and find him.

114
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:25,160
Lu Feng, what on earth
are you trying to do?

115
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,120
I have to go back and find him.

116
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,800
I need to get the story straight.

117
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,440
He couldn't have done this.

118
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:31,520
Find him?

119
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,679
You've gotten older, but you
haven't gotten any smarter.

120
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:36,440
Do you think it's that
easy to find someone?

121
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:40,240
With the Zhuo family's power and influence,
hiding someone is child's play for them.

122
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,760
Lu Feng, I'm telling you,

123
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,480
you're not going anywhere today.

124
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:46,560
I've already signed the agreement.

125
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:48,160
Right now, the Lu family and I...

126
00:13:48,161 --> 00:13:49,776
have absolutely nothing
to do with each other.

127
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:50,920
If I want to find him,

128
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:52,440
that's my own business.

129
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,720
You have no right to control me.

130
00:13:57,920 --> 00:13:58,920
What did you say?

131
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:02,599
I said you have no right to control me.

132
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:03,920
Are you out of your mind?

133
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:06,120
He's already married.

134
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,720
And he did it behind your back.

135
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:10,000
He doesn't love you at all.

136
00:14:10,880 --> 00:14:12,200
You're throwing away your future,

137
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:13,360
your family,

138
00:14:13,680 --> 00:14:15,360
all for a man like that?

139
00:14:19,640 --> 00:14:20,800
That's my business.

140
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:23,440
Sis.

141
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,080
I suddenly realize...

142
00:14:27,800 --> 00:14:29,200
you're just like Dad.

143
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,360
I just really...

144
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,360
really love him.

145
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,000
Just go.

146
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:47,520
Go.

147
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:56,720
Let him go.

148
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:05,160
Don't worry.

149
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:06,560
I've contacted my friends.

150
00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:08,680
Their hospital is very experienced.

151
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:10,840
They'll definitely be able
to cure Cheng Yi-chen.

152
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,000
Qin Lang.

153
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,920
I'm leaving Cheng Yi-chen in your hands.

154
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:15,840
As for my mom,

155
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:17,640
I'll be here.

156
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,720
She just needs to focus on getting better.

157
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:21,080
Okay.

158
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:10,120
Is that Xiao Chen?

159
00:16:13,680 --> 00:16:14,880
Mom.

160
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:17,880
It's me, Xiao Chen.

161
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:35,160
Why are you so thin?

162
00:16:47,040 --> 00:16:48,120
My son.

163
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:54,680
I'm sorry.

164
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:04,360
Mom.

165
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:07,760
Mom.

166
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:10,880
Mom.

167
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:14,280
Mom.

168
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:18,480
Mom.

169
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:21,040
Mom.

170
00:17:22,120 --> 00:17:23,120
Mom.

171
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:26,200
Cheng Yi-chen.

172
00:18:29,040 --> 00:18:30,280
Your mother... she's gone.

173
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:32,320
There's no point in you going back now.

174
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,000
Cheng Yi-chen.

175
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:35,200
Calm down.

176
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:36,760
Cheng Yi-chen.

177
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:14,520
You did great on your exams, son.

178
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:15,920
You've made me so proud.

179
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:17,200
Great, just great.

180
00:19:17,201 --> 00:19:19,400
That's my boy.

181
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:54,120
Son, come and eat.

182
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:58,280
Life right now...

183
00:19:58,880 --> 00:20:01,920
is like a fast-paced,
illogical, black-and-white dream.

184
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:05,160
My hardworking father,

185
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:07,680
my caring mother,

186
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:10,920
my little brother who adored me.

187
00:20:12,800 --> 00:20:15,600
When did they all just... disappear?

188
00:20:58,480 --> 00:20:59,959
Once we get to the new city,

189
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:01,240
everything will be okay.

190
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:26,200
Let me.

191
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:27,640
Thanks.

192
00:22:16,520 --> 00:22:17,520
Qin Lang.

193
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:19,160
I'm married now.

194
00:22:20,320 --> 00:22:21,880
And I've decided to move away

195
00:22:22,080 --> 00:22:23,240
to start over.

196
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:25,520
I sold the old house.

197
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:28,680
I transferred all the money
to Cheng Yi-chen's account.

198
00:22:29,280 --> 00:22:30,280
From now on,

199
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:32,200
I'm leaving Cheng Yi-chen to you.

200
00:22:33,360 --> 00:22:34,680
For the time being,

201
00:22:35,040 --> 00:22:37,040
I'll contact you if I need anything.

202
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:38,760
Don't try to find me,

203
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:40,680
and don't worry about me.

204
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:44,240
Lu Feng will definitely
come looking for me again.

205
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:45,120
Xiao Chen.

206
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,200
And I...

207
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:47,360
Xiao Chen.

208
00:22:47,361 --> 00:22:49,000
I really don't know how to face him.

209
00:22:50,280 --> 00:22:51,959
You should try to stay away from him, too.

210
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:52,960
Xiao Chen.

211
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:10,120
Mr. Lu.

212
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:11,200
Where's Xiao Chen?

213
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:13,800
He quit.

214
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,680
Even if you find him, what then?

215
00:23:30,520 --> 00:23:32,440
From the moment he got married,

216
00:23:33,680 --> 00:23:35,120
he already gave up on you.

217
00:23:41,840 --> 00:23:42,840
Lu Feng.

218
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:44,880
You need to understand.

219
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:48,880
If you truly want to be the
master of your own destiny,

220
00:23:50,720 --> 00:23:52,600
you have to learn to bide your time.

221
00:23:54,080 --> 00:23:56,320
Wait until you're strong enough to fly.

222
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:40,960
Good night.

223
00:24:41,040 --> 00:24:42,040
Get some rest.

224
00:26:45,305 --> 00:26:47,591
Five years later.

225
00:27:02,520 --> 00:27:03,160
Let's begin.

226
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:04,480
Okay.

227
00:27:04,560 --> 00:27:06,800
According to our market research,

228
00:27:22,360 --> 00:27:22,880
Well,

229
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:24,120
I'll be going then.

230
00:27:24,960 --> 00:27:26,440
Leaving? I'm going home too.

231
00:27:27,080 --> 00:27:28,240
He's been waiting for you.

232
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:33,160
Mr. Cheng.

233
00:27:33,560 --> 00:27:35,800
After all, we are still legally married.

234
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:37,600
This kind of behavior...

235
00:27:37,920 --> 00:27:39,480
is disrespectful to all three of us.

236
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:43,080
Let's wait until we have
time to finalize the divorce.

237
00:27:45,760 --> 00:27:46,760
Yichen.

238
00:27:47,233 --> 00:27:48,993
I think it's time for us to move on.

239
00:27:51,160 --> 00:27:52,160
I'm sorry.

240
00:27:52,240 --> 00:27:54,680
I've held you back all these years.

241
00:27:55,760 --> 00:27:56,880
Who's holding who back?

242
00:27:57,960 --> 00:27:59,680
If it weren't for you these past few years,

243
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:02,600
I wouldn't have been able to establish
myself at the company so quickly.

244
00:28:02,840 --> 00:28:03,840
Besides,

245
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:05,360
if it weren't for these five years,

246
00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:06,960
how would I have known...

247
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,800
that we're actually
better off as friends?

248
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:12,600
We'll always be friends.

249
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:14,960
I think so too.

250
00:28:40,480 --> 00:28:42,279
A new generation of entrepreneurs

251
00:28:42,280 --> 00:28:43,520
who grew up in the internet age

252
00:28:43,720 --> 00:28:45,719
are reshaping philanthropy

253
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:47,400
with their unique and innovative thinking.

254
00:28:47,520 --> 00:28:47,920
Today,

255
00:28:48,080 --> 00:28:50,879
we have the honor of interviewing
a pioneering entrepreneur,

256
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:52,559
the founder of Feng Yang Technology,

257
00:28:52,560 --> 00:28:53,360
Mr. Lu Feng.

258
00:28:53,480 --> 00:28:54,879
We've invited him to talk to us about

259
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:56,040
his philanthropic philosophy.

260
00:28:56,120 --> 00:28:56,760
Hello, everyone.

261
00:28:57,080 --> 00:28:59,040
I'm Lu Feng, the founder of FC Company.

262
00:28:59,360 --> 00:29:01,480
FC Company has always been a leader

263
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:03,160
in emerging technologies.

264
00:29:03,185 --> 00:29:04,361
And giving back to the community

265
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:06,520
is one of our company's core principles.

266
00:29:30,799 --> 00:29:32,785
[After all these years he stays
looking up Lu Feng on the internet]

267
00:29:40,280 --> 00:29:41,440
You want to quit?

268
00:29:41,920 --> 00:29:42,920
Why?

269
00:29:43,360 --> 00:29:44,640
Is it because we got divorced?

270
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:45,960
No.

271
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:48,400
Then why?

272
00:29:49,040 --> 00:29:51,400
You've worked so hard to
establish yourself at the company.

273
00:29:52,040 --> 00:29:53,920
Have you been too stressed or tired lately?

274
00:29:54,240 --> 00:29:55,240
No, Zhuo Lan.

275
00:29:58,240 --> 00:29:59,240
I just...

276
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:01,520
want to do something else.

277
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:05,880
Alright.

278
00:30:06,280 --> 00:30:07,280
I respect your decision.

279
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:08,680
But remember,

280
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:10,000
no matter what,

281
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:12,440
there will always be a place for you here.

282
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:54,120
Hello, who are you looking for?

283
00:30:56,520 --> 00:30:58,200
I'm looking for Lu Feng.

284
00:30:59,320 --> 00:31:00,600
Do you have an appointment?

285
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:02,920
No.

286
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:06,000
But I'm an old...

287
00:31:06,360 --> 00:31:07,360
friend of his.

288
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:08,720
I'm sorry.

289
00:31:08,840 --> 00:31:10,400
You can't go in without an appointment.

290
00:31:10,760 --> 00:31:12,000
I really am his friend.

291
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:21,240
Another 'friend'.

292
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:22,800
Ever since the boss was in the news,

293
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:25,296
people claiming to be his friend have
been showing up one after another.

294
00:31:25,320 --> 00:31:26,000
Thinking they can just come and go
as they please.

295
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:28,720
Do they think this is a public market?

296
00:31:29,280 --> 00:31:32,200
If you're really his friend, why didn't
you make an appointment yourself?

297
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:46,920
Hey.

298
00:31:47,080 --> 00:31:48,080
Are you okay?

299
00:31:48,520 --> 00:31:49,080
I'm fine.

300
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:50,240
I'm sorry.

301
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,520
Did you hurt your leg?

302
00:31:52,680 --> 00:31:54,960
Maybe we should go to the
hospital to get it checked out.

303
00:31:58,080 --> 00:31:58,720
It's fine.

304
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:00,040
No need.

305
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:10,856
Is something wrong with your laptop?

306
00:32:10,880 --> 00:32:11,880
It's broken.

307
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:15,240
I have very important files
on it that I haven't exported.

308
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:17,480
How about this?

309
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:18,840
Let's go to the hospital first.
I know how to fix computers.

310
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:21,320
Get in the car, I'll take a look for you.

311
00:32:32,120 --> 00:32:33,560
Did it get wet?

312
00:32:33,840 --> 00:32:34,320
Yes.

313
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:36,360
It got wet last night.

314
00:32:36,480 --> 00:32:37,840
I called customer service,

315
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:39,336
and they told me to leave
it upside down overnight.

316
00:32:39,360 --> 00:32:40,536
They said it would be fine the next day.

317
00:32:40,560 --> 00:32:42,400
But now it won't turn on.

318
00:32:42,640 --> 00:32:44,056
The motherboard is probably corroded.

319
00:32:44,080 --> 00:32:45,520
It can't be fixed in this condition.

320
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:46,960
Then what do I do?

321
00:32:47,320 --> 00:32:49,136
My thesis that I've been
writing for a month is still on it.

322
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:50,160
Don't worry.

323
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:51,000
We can go to a repair shop

324
00:32:51,120 --> 00:32:53,120
and just retrieve the data
from the storage drive.

325
00:32:54,280 --> 00:32:55,880
Come on, let's go to the hospital first.

326
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:57,360
Let's go to the repair shop first.

327
00:32:59,080 --> 00:33:00,080
Okay.

328
00:33:03,160 --> 00:33:04,600
By the way, what's your name?

329
00:33:06,120 --> 00:33:07,120
My name is Ke Lo.

330
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:09,520
Ke Lo.

331
00:33:13,040 --> 00:33:14,520
Then I'll see you again tomorrow.

332
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:16,520
Okay, goodbye.

333
00:33:20,120 --> 00:33:22,680
I've transferred all your
files to this hard drive.

334
00:33:23,040 --> 00:33:23,640
I asked around.

335
00:33:23,760 --> 00:33:25,576
It would cost several
thousand to repair the laptop.

336
00:33:25,600 --> 00:33:26,760
I don't think it's worth it.

337
00:33:27,080 --> 00:33:27,840
It's okay.

338
00:33:28,080 --> 00:33:29,160
As long as I have my files.

339
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:33,560
Are you still looking for a job?

340
00:33:33,880 --> 00:33:34,880
Yeah.

341
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:36,480
How's your leg?
Does it still hurt?

342
00:33:38,120 --> 00:33:38,840
It's fine.

343
00:33:39,120 --> 00:33:40,120
It doesn't hurt at all.

344
00:33:40,880 --> 00:33:43,280
Maybe you should still go to
the hospital to get it checked.

345
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:44,880
Look, it's really fine.

346
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:47,400
By the way,

347
00:33:47,520 --> 00:33:49,400
I know the boss of a tech company,

348
00:33:49,640 --> 00:33:51,400
and they're hiring right now.

349
00:33:51,600 --> 00:33:52,879
You're so capable.

350
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:54,080
You'll definitely get the job.

351
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:55,240
I took the liberty of

352
00:33:55,360 --> 00:33:57,360
sending them the resume
from your back seat.

353
00:33:58,360 --> 00:33:59,840
How do you know I'm capable?

354
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:01,480
Isn't it obvious?

355
00:34:01,600 --> 00:34:02,400
My laptop...

356
00:34:02,520 --> 00:34:04,256
you knew what was
wrong with it right away.

357
00:34:04,280 --> 00:34:05,879
Plus, you're kind,

358
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:06,560
upright,

359
00:34:06,680 --> 00:34:07,640
and responsible.
Okay, okay.

360
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:10,000
Don't overdo it.

361
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:13,600
I'm serious.

362
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:16,080
Why don't we go check it out now?

363
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:20,400
Let's go, let's go.

364
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:24,480
We're here.

365
00:34:24,560 --> 00:34:25,560
This is it.

366
00:34:28,120 --> 00:34:30,480
The boss you know... his name is Lu Feng?

367
00:34:31,600 --> 00:34:32,600
How did you know?

368
00:34:33,680 --> 00:34:34,880
This place isn't right for me.

369
00:34:35,560 --> 00:34:37,440
You should at least meet
him before you decide.

370
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:38,800
No.

371
00:34:38,840 --> 00:34:39,840
I already told my...

372
00:34:40,240 --> 00:34:41,600
I already told Mr. Lu.

373
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:43,136
And he's very impressed with you.

374
00:34:43,160 --> 00:34:44,560
He wants to interview you himself.

375
00:34:45,080 --> 00:34:45,920
Normally, this kind of thing

376
00:34:45,921 --> 00:34:47,640
is handled by his subordinates.

377
00:34:48,520 --> 00:34:49,600
He knows it's me?

378
00:34:50,720 --> 00:34:51,720
Yeah.

379
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:53,440
Come on, let's go.

380
00:34:57,800 --> 00:34:58,800
Nervous?

381
00:34:59,600 --> 00:35:00,720
It's okay.

382
00:35:12,720 --> 00:35:14,080
Have a good chat. Mr. Lu.

383
00:35:34,920 --> 00:35:35,920
Yichen.

384
00:35:38,720 --> 00:35:39,720
Long time no see.

385
00:35:46,280 --> 00:35:48,800
I thought it was just
someone with the same name.

386
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:50,440
I can't believe it's really you.

387
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:54,760
Have a seat.

388
00:36:03,720 --> 00:36:05,400
I didn't expect you to be in Xincheng too.

389
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:09,720
I thought you would've
come to find me sooner.

390
00:36:13,240 --> 00:36:14,240
I did look for you.

391
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,176
But I didn't have an appointment.

392
00:36:16,200 --> 00:36:17,200
So...

393
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:19,320
So you found Ke Lo.

394
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:23,520
Using him was a pretty clever move.

395
00:36:23,680 --> 00:36:25,199
I didn't use Ke Lo. I...

396
00:36:25,200 --> 00:36:26,280
Ke Lo is just a kid.

397
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:27,480
He's naive

398
00:36:27,960 --> 00:36:29,080
and very enthusiastic.

399
00:36:30,040 --> 00:36:31,400
Most importantly,

400
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:33,600
he's very close to me.

401
00:36:37,240 --> 00:36:39,440
It really could make
things a lot easier for you.

402
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:49,880
By the way.

403
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:54,240
Ke Lo said you wanted
to work at my company.

404
00:36:54,680 --> 00:36:56,280
Are you still at your old job?

405
00:37:03,040 --> 00:37:04,200
At my company,

406
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,880
for an employee at your level,

407
00:37:06,040 --> 00:37:07,256
the salary is usually around...

408
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:08,280
No.

409
00:37:09,080 --> 00:37:10,080
What's wrong?

410
00:37:11,200 --> 00:37:12,560
Worried the salary is too low?

411
00:37:16,880 --> 00:37:17,880
How about this.

412
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:20,880
Since we're old classmates,

413
00:37:21,720 --> 00:37:24,000
you can name your price.

414
00:37:24,760 --> 00:37:25,760
Don't be shy.

415
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:29,880
As long as it's within a reasonable range,

416
00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:31,240
I'll be sure to meet it.

417
00:37:32,680 --> 00:37:33,680
That won't be necessary.

418
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:35,400
I've already found a job.

419
00:37:39,720 --> 00:37:41,040
Then what are you here for today?

420
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:53,280
If there's nothing else,

421
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:55,560
please don't waste my time.

422
00:37:58,280 --> 00:37:59,640
I have a client meeting soon.

423
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:02,800
Then I'll be going.

424
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:07,920
So? How did it go?

425
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:10,240
I really don't want to work here.

426
00:38:11,160 --> 00:38:12,160
Why?

427
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:14,080
Is it the salary?

428
00:38:14,160 --> 00:38:15,440
Or some other reason?

429
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:17,360
Ke Lo.

430
00:38:18,640 --> 00:38:19,640
Come in.
